  <brief_title>Action Observation in Knee Replacement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Self-administered Action Observation Treatment Enhance the Efficacy of Inpatient Rehabilitation After Total Knee Replacement: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
